<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381000' id='t-381000'>And if you look, you can see them happening, already beginning to emerge.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='384000' id='t-384000'>The World Trade Organization: treaty-based organization,</span>
