</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429000' id='t-429000'>So there's my first message,</span>
