 8:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='500000' id='t-500000'>My guess is, for what it's worth,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='502000' id='t-502000'>is that the United States will remain</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504000' id='t-504000'>the most powerful nation on earth</span>
